cdata.name: Reality Clash
cdata.desc:
RCC Gold Coins is an Ethereum-based token that will serve as an in-game currency for what is described as "most comprehensive and advanced social augmented reality combat game in the market", Reality Cash, which will be available for iPhone and Android. 

RCC Gold coins also give users the opportunity to acquire weapons and armory that no one else will have

• The token sale. All in-game content will be ERC-20 tokenized with a Blockchain-based trust list.
